          <h1>Web Design and Accessibility: Key Takeaways from <em>Headspur</em> and <em>Blacksmith Agency</em></h1>
          <p>Web design should be accessible, and it is not a nice to have; rather, it is an absolute must when it comes to this aspect. That is why <a href="https://www.headspur.it/">Headspur</a> partnered with <a href="http://blacksmith.agency">Blacksmith Agency</a> to make sure every website that they create would be accessible to every user of any ability. The partnership ultimately married strategic expertise from Headspur with the creativity and technical know-how of <a href="https://blacksmith.agency/web-design-los-angeles/">Blacksmith Agency's Los Angeles design team</a> in crafting websites that are beautiful but at the same time inclusive and user-friendly.</p>
